OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773626592
OL,3,CTownhouse: Nail salons overlooked by
OL,4,Cmale-led investment for decades
OL,6,FNail salons are next in line for
OL,7,FStarbucks-style expansion after
OL,8,Fdecades of being overlooked by
OL,9,Finvestors, the boss of the UK's
OL,10,Flargest luxury chain has said, after
OL,11,Fclinching a #130 million valuation.
OL,13,FTownhouse, which runs 40 luxury nail
OL,14,Fsalons in the UK, said it was
OL,15,Ftargeting hundreds of new franchised
OL,16,Fsites after securing backing from the
OL,17,FUS private equity firm behind the
OL,18,FBurger King and Tim Horton chains in
OL,19,FChina.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773626592
OL,3,CTownhouse: Nail salons overlooked by
OL,4,Cmale-led investment for decades
OL,6,FThe new investment from Cartesian
OL,7,FCapital will propel the expansion of
OL,8,Fthe business, which was founded in
OL,9,F2018 by Juanita Huber-Millet and
OL,10,Fheaded up by her husband and chief
OL,11,Fexecutive Jonathan Millet.
OL,13,FMr Millet said it was capturing a
OL,14,Fturning point in the nail care
OL,15,Findustry, which is highly fragmented
OL,16,Fand has been typically under-invested
OL,17,Fin compared with other services.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773626592
OL,3,CTownhouse: Nail salons overlooked by
OL,4,Cmale-led investment for decades
OL,6,F"I think there is probably an element
OL,7,Fof beauty services overall being
OL,8,Foverlooked," he told the Press
OL,9,FAssociation.
OL,11,F"I would say there is a little bit of
OL,12,Fan element of, historically, 20, 30
OL,13,Fyears ago, finance and capital being
OL,14,Fvery dominated by men, and this being
OL,15,Fa sector that primarily serves women.
OL,17,F"So if you're a male private equity
OL,18,Finvestor maybe 15 or 20 years ago then
OL,19,Fmaybe it wasn't front and centre of
OL,20,Fyour mind as something to invest in."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@LO]sD@AOUyD@AOU|D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773626592
OL,3,CTownhouse: Nail salons overlooked by
OL,4,Cmale-led investment for decades
OL,6,FHe made comparisons with industries
OL,7,Fsuch as coffee houses, hotels, gyms
OL,8,Fand sandwich shops, which have all
OL,9,Fexpanded with the emergence of chains
OL,10,Fover recent decades.
OL,12,FOther parts of the beauty salon
OL,13,Fsector, such as waxing and massages,
OL,14,Fhave started to grow with brands
OL,15,F"delivering that Starbucks-esque
OL,16,Fexperience" after years of the beauty
OL,17,Fservices industry "lagging behind".
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@KO]yD@SOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773626592
OL,3,CTownhouse: Nail salons overlooked by
OL,4,Cmale-led investment for decades
OL,6,FMeanwhile, there are no major nail
OL,7,Fsalon chains in the UK, with Townhouse
OL,8,Fentering a market that is typically
OL,9,Fled by independent and boutique shops.
OL,11,FMr Millet also said the nail industry
OL,12,Fhas been plagued with poor working
OL,13,Fconditions for staff, a lack of
OL,14,Femployment contracts, and even cases
OL,15,Fof modern slavery.
OL,17,F"In our industry there has
OL,18,Fhistorically been quite a lot of
OL,19,Fexploitation of workers," he told the
OL,20,FPress Association.
OL,26,@yD@AOU{D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773626592
OL,3,CTownhouse: Nail salons overlooked by
OL,4,Cmale-led investment for decades
OL,6,F"When Covid hit, there were a lot of
OL,7,Fpeople in the industry who didn't have
OL,8,Fcontracts, who were just being paid
OL,9,Fcash in hand, so they didn't get
OL,10,Fgovernment relief.
OL,12,F"And we still see a lot of people, as
OL,13,Fwe're recruiting, who have worked in
OL,14,Fthe industry and not had contracts `
OL,15,Fall the way through to, less pervasive
OL,16,Fbut there, some elements of
OL,17,Ftrafficking and indentured labour."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773626592
OL,3,CTownhouse: Nail salons overlooked by
OL,4,Cmale-led investment for decades
OL,6,FTownhouse says it offers its nail
OL,7,Ftechnicians above-market pay, private
OL,8,Fhealthcare, paid leave and structured
OL,9,Fcareer progression, including in the
OL,10,FUS, where it currently has a handful
OL,11,Fof stores.
OL,13,FThe business has signed up major
OL,14,Ffranchisees, with about 149 sites
OL,15,Fcommitted over the next five years,
OL,16,Fand another roughly 350 in advanced
OL,17,Fnegotiations.
OL,19,FIt said this would bring the chain to
OL,20,Fabout 500 salons internationally and
OL,21,Fcreate an estimated 5,400 jobs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773626592
OL,3,CTownhouse: Nail salons overlooked by
OL,4,Cmale-led investment for decades
OL,6,FMr Millet said Townhouse sits in the
OL,7,F"premium to luxury part of the market"
OL,8,Fwith prices ranging from about #30 to
OL,9,F#100 for each treatment.
OL,11,FHe suggested that nail care was "more
OL,12,Fresilient" to economic downturns,
OL,13,Fadding: "We see people who may need to
OL,14,Fcut down in some parts of their lives
OL,15,Freally keep up their beauty regime
OL,16,Fbecause it's that small moment of
OL,17,Fluxury."
OL,19,F"It's not affordable for everyone, but
OL,20,Fit's a price that people are willing
OL,21,Fto pay."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@fO]sD@aOUtD@JO]uD@IOUyD@HO]{D@
OL,26,AAOU}D@HO]
