CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773626592
OL,3,CTownhouse: Nail salons overlooked by
OL,4,Cmale-led investment for decades
OL,6,FThe chain is predominately focused in
OL,7,FLondon but has also opened salons in
OL,8,Fcities including Manchester, Bristol
OL,9,Fand Leeds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
